# Enforce LF line endings for all text files across every platform.
# `text=auto` lets Git detect text vs binary; `eol=lf` checks text out as LF
# on Windows too, so the working tree matches the repo and no CRLF creeps back
# (core.autocrlf is false in this repo, so this file is the single source of truth).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types: never touch their bytes / never normalize EOL.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.gguf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary

